						               													<description>The first board game that rewards your knowledge!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;World Challenge Game is a game where all players will answer questions and will conquer countries simultaneously. Depending on the chosen game mode &amp;quot;Conqueror or Attack&amp;quot; the game will end sooner or later. Fight to conquer the world and show that you are the one who knows the most! Answer questions, think carefully about the territories you want to conquer and learn while you prove that you are the best in World Challenge Game.&amp;#10; Choose one of two game modes:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;- Conqueror, where you conquer as many countries as possible before the end of the game or Raid, where you attack and win the countries conquered by other players to take over the entire continent. In this mode you can conquer a country that another player has won.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;On each turn, a player will take a card and choose one of the two existing questions, which they must read aloud, along with the four answers. The other participants will write on their card the answer which they consider correct, marking an &amp;quot;X&amp;quot; in the options A, B, C or D. When everyone has answered the question, the answers will be revealed, starting with the player to the left of the one who read the question. If the answer is correct, the player can place a conquest token in an available border country and the same for the rest of the players.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The Conqueror game will automatically end once the last country on the continent is conquered. At that time, the countries that each player has conquered will be counted, so the player with the most countries conquered will be the winner of the game. If there are two or more players who have the same maximum number of conquered countries, questions will be read to them as a tiebreaker. Players who cannot answer the question lose.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;- The Attack game will end when there is only one player left on the continent and they will be crowned the winner. If the question cards run out, the game would end and the one with the most countries would win. There is also the option in case you want to continue the game, you can use the questions available in the APP, choosing the &amp;quot;Board game questions&amp;quot; section.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
